'''世界保護區委員會'''（{{lang-en|'''W'''orld '''C'''ommission on '''P'''rotected '''A'''reas}}，縮寫'''WCPA'''）是[[世界自然保護聯盟|世界自然保護聯盟]]（IUCN）的六个委员会之一。<ref name="IUCN">{{cite web |url=http://cms.iucn.org/about/union/commissions/wcpa/index.cfm |title=IUCN - World Commission on Protected Areas |publisher=IUCN |accessdate=2008-09-07 |archive-date=2012-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120910074838/http://cms.iucn.org/about/union/commissions/wcpa/index.cfm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>.

